# Email Configuration
# For Gmail SMTP (recommended for development)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password
FROM_EMAIL=noreply@bookbite.com

# Instructions for Gmail:
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Gmail account
# 2. Go to Google Account settings > Security > App passwords
# 3. Generate an app password for "Mail"
# 4. Use that app password (not your regular password) in SMTP_PASSWORD
# 5. Copy this file to .env and update with your credentials

# Alternative free email services:
# Mailgun: https://www.mailgun.com/ (5000 emails/month free)
# SendGrid: https://sendgrid.com/ (100 emails/day free)
# Brevo: https://www.brevo.com/ (300 emails/day free)
